; tests/knowledge-ingest-band.fk — the ingest-distill circuit (how human knowledge enters the mind), four-way.
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk form-stdlib/knowledge-ingest.fk
;
; Verdict 11111: a deep fear-free teaching freezes into durable memory (body); a deep but fearful one is witnessed
; only, never frozen (the fear-free-ice law); a shallow one composts (only the translation-invariant meaning
; enters); the deep fear-free unit ingests deeper than the shallow; and the fearful deep unit is still SEEN --
; fear is removed before ice, never before sight. Frozen=body, witnessed=liquid, composted=neither.
(do (knowledge-ingest-check))
